column11:
  In this paper, we give a new approach to classify all simple Harish-Chandra
modules for the N=1 Ramond algebra based on the so called A-cover theory
developed in \cite{BF}

column5:
24 pages, 11 figures, 6 tables; version 3 of this paper;
  significantly reduced extraneous explanations and technical details and
  addressed some points raised by others; submitted to Nucl. Phys. A
